                    <ul>
                        <li>“Daily” means this is someone you communicate with daily.</li>
                        <li>“Weekly” indicates this is someone you usually interact with and communicate on a weekly basis.</li>
                        <li>“Less often” indicates this is someone you speak to infrequently.</li>
